{"tid":1851713,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔封關  俾一千個口罩你都冇用！","createTime":"2020-01-30T06:40:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T06:45:57.000Z","uid":73959,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"48cc18b82913bba43fc98fe8a3490bcc5637d26f","tid":1851713,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:40:22.000Z","msg":"首先講咗好多次<br />\n戴口罩<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔係萬能</span><br />\n戴唔啱一樣奶嘢<br />\n甚至正確啲嚟講 戴口罩只係保障其他人<br />\n因為你唔知自己有冇病 戴口罩就可以預防啲飛沫傳播<br />\n<br />\n我唔係不食人間煙火<br />\n我一樣買口罩戴口罩<br />\n但係我見到全世界咁瘋狂嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n我想大家<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">冷靜啲 諗清楚</span><br />\n要防止呢個病毒散播<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最緊要都係源頭</span></span><br />\n大家見到而家確診嘅 都係內地人<br />\n一日唔封關 一隻又一隻嘅移動病毒走入嚟香港<br />\n<br />\n就好似香港人得3個煲蓋但要琴10個煲<br />\n而家大家都瘋狂搵緊煲蓋<br />\n但其實煲嘅數量一直增加<br />\n你搵幾多個煲蓋都冇用<br />\n最重要係<br />\n嗰煲會死人<br />\n<br />\n所以我懇請大家<br />\n將個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>focus</strong></span></span>擺返係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">封關</span></strong></span>到<br />\n擺返係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">罷工</span></strong></span>到<br />\n擺返係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">前線醫護</span></strong></span>到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔封關  俾一千個口罩你都冇用！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"358cfb2ebbdef98620481b3e9c445bd98f967c31","tid":1851713,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:45:57.000Z","msg":"上街表達意見 要求政府封關 繼而五大訴求<br />\n永遠不忘初衷"}]}